{"tid":1109680,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好心香港啲自助付款執柒曬佢啦","createTime":"2019-04-16T10:44:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T09:03:21.000Z","uid":120458,"like":63,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"638a8fbe0dedee4f700bc5d6f2c2be5cc7c8a50c","tid":1109680,"uid":120458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:44:50.000Z","msg":"岩岩去咗屈臣氏買Vibrator諗住今晚同女朋友玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我專登揀間有自助付款既屈臣氏買，咁俾錢都冇咁老尷<br />\n正當我行咗去個自助收銀機 嘟咗件貨<br />\n點知有條仆街後生仔店員懶醒，即刻衝過黎問我：「我幫你啦」<br />\n嗰刻我真係好想打柒佢 <br />\n我又唔係啲廢老中年阿叔 我駛撚你幫我手？<br />\n條仆街望一望Cashier個螢幕<br />\n個Screen大大隻字寫住：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dXmrEaf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXmrEaf.png&h=db672e03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢望咗一眼 已經深知不妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚心啲自助付款機如果唔係真係自助付款就咪撚放出嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次都係online store買算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ba2cb5f6a5a0ac0b9bea6cd5e1b048310d5be6","tid":1109680,"uid":161374,"like":24,"dislike":8,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:45:52.000Z","msg":"咁都怕羞就唔好出街啦，毒撚"},{"pid":"d1e2b576ee1adf455dd32ae01688ced6b1fc5fcb","tid":1109680,"uid":27458,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T10:46:52.000Z","msg":"店員想同樓主玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f336bbd50104cdb4a6ca88b1d43f4ac4c36fcb","tid":1109680,"uid":120458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91ba2cb5f6a5a0ac0b9bea6cd5e1b048310d5be6","tid":1109680,"uid":161374,"like":24,"dislike":8,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTi